WEBVTT

01:30.960 --> 01:35.039
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.700 --> 01:39.070
[2006]

01:47.039 --> 01:48.100
Miss, you're here.

01:48.590 --> 01:49.789
Which bunk are you in?

01:50.039 --> 01:51.310
Uh... No. 6.

01:51.840 --> 01:52.840
No. 6 is over here.

01:53.509 --> 01:54.570
We're in this bunk.

01:54.840 --> 01:55.870
We'll be classmates from now on.

01:55.870 --> 01:57.229
Let's look out for each other.

01:57.229 --> 01:57.700
Is that heavy?

01:57.700 --> 01:58.479
Do you need a hand?

01:58.479 --> 01:59.039
No, thanks!

01:59.039 --> 01:59.840
I can manage.

02:00.200 --> 02:00.860
Be careful.

02:01.070 --> 02:01.430
Okay.

02:02.840 --> 02:04.170
Miss, what's your name?

02:04.200 --> 02:05.040
Where are you from?

02:05.040 --> 02:06.870
Didn't your parents come with you?

02:06.870 --> 02:07.430
Mom,

02:07.430 --> 02:08.680
let her put her things down

02:08.680 --> 02:10.680
before you start your questioning.

02:11.000 --> 02:11.840
Hello, Auntie.

02:11.840 --> 02:13.100
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

02:13.680 --> 02:15.560
I'm from Xiangsheng.

02:15.630 --> 02:17.840
My parents work in geology,

02:17.840 --> 02:18.630
and they're away on a business trip,

02:18.630 --> 02:19.690
so I came by myself.

02:21.560 --> 02:22.470
Hello, Xiaolan.

02:22.470 --> 02:23.310
I'm Zhao Lin.

02:23.560 --> 02:25.360
I'm from Ganzhou, Jiangxi.

02:25.870 --> 02:26.680
Sorry about that.

02:26.680 --> 02:28.240
Both my parents are teachers,

02:28.240 --> 02:29.470
so they tend to talk a lot.

02:29.470 --> 02:30.070
It's fine.

02:30.630 --> 02:31.560
Do you need help?

02:31.630 --> 02:32.090
No need.

02:32.280 --> 02:32.590
No need.

02:32.590 --> 02:33.590
Your parents' work

02:33.590 --> 02:34.680
must be quite demanding.

02:34.680 --> 02:36.000
You're so considerate.

02:36.000 --> 02:36.660
Look at you—

02:36.910 --> 02:38.630
you can't even make your own bed,

02:38.630 --> 02:40.000
and you're already a university student.

02:40.000 --> 02:41.150
Mom, stop it.

02:41.150 --> 02:42.470
Don't embarrass me.

02:43.710 --> 02:45.710
I fabricated my family background,

02:46.000 --> 02:47.860
thinking I could start a new life.

02:48.680 --> 02:50.940
But the lies only dressed up the surface—

02:51.590 --> 02:52.790
the substance of life

02:53.310 --> 02:55.640
still needs to be filled with real effort.

03:02.040 --> 03:05.270
[Episode 24: A Fabricated Life]

03:06.310 --> 03:08.470
Anyone who's found gold,

03:08.710 --> 03:10.970
please line up to register and turn it in!

03:11.190 --> 03:12.710
Thank you for your cooperation!

03:12.710 --> 03:13.750
Thank you, everyone!

03:13.750 --> 03:14.610
Hello, Ms. Xia.

03:14.680 --> 03:15.310
We heard gold

03:15.310 --> 03:16.520
was discovered here.

03:16.630 --> 03:17.960
What are your thoughts on this?

03:17.960 --> 03:19.150
All found gold must be turned in!

03:19.150 --> 03:20.430
Follow me!

03:20.450 --> 03:21.520
Come on, let's go!

03:21.520 --> 03:23.050
Let's go take back our gold!

03:23.470 --> 03:23.930
Come on!

03:24.120 --> 03:25.720
No one is allowed to keep any!

03:26.310 --> 03:27.280
What are you doing?

03:27.280 --> 03:28.210
Stop, all of you!

03:28.840 --> 03:29.400
Calm down!

03:29.400 --> 03:30.520
That's my family's gold!

03:30.520 --> 03:31.190
Calm down!

03:31.190 --> 03:33.360
It's my family's gold!

03:33.360 --> 03:34.890
It's our Luo family's gold!

03:35.030 --> 03:35.750
It's mine!

03:39.190 --> 03:40.250
Grandpa? Grandpa!

03:40.880 --> 03:41.410
Careful.

03:41.800 --> 03:43.079
Get him to the hospital now!

03:43.079 --> 03:43.880
Hurry, hurry!

03:45.850 --> 03:46.630
As you can see,

03:46.630 --> 03:47.680
I am currently at

03:47.680 --> 03:49.710
the Golden Sands Pool project
construction site.

03:49.710 --> 03:51.470
According to police reports,

03:51.710 --> 03:53.240
a total of 627 grams of gold

03:53.240 --> 03:54.870
was found in the area.

03:55.400 --> 03:57.460
Six hundred and twenty-seven grams.

03:57.710 --> 03:59.310
We buried a kilogram of gold—

03:59.520 --> 04:01.030
the loss is quite significant.

04:01.030 --> 04:02.750
Yuesheng's geological survey department

04:02.750 --> 04:04.000
is about to conduct

04:04.030 --> 04:05.000
a professional

04:05.000 --> 04:06.030
assessment here

04:06.050 --> 04:08.280
to determine whether there is a gold mine

04:08.280 --> 04:10.150
underground with commercial value.

04:10.150 --> 04:10.750
Ms. Xia,

04:10.870 --> 04:12.400
your eye for property is amazing!

04:12.400 --> 04:14.310
This really is a feng shui treasure land.

04:14.310 --> 04:14.960
Now,

04:14.960 --> 04:16.820
Golden Sands Pool is well-known!

04:17.160 --> 04:18.190
Who would have thought back then

04:18.190 --> 04:19.380
that such a stinky bamboo ditch

04:19.380 --> 04:20.839
actually contained gold?

04:21.600 --> 04:23.040
Qi Hang's first project

04:23.160 --> 04:24.290
is about to take off.

04:25.510 --> 04:26.630
Now that the name is out there,

04:26.630 --> 04:28.490
the money will naturally follow.

04:28.630 --> 04:30.240
Xiaolan is amazing.

04:30.710 --> 04:32.110
There really is gold-bearing sand.

04:32.110 --> 04:32.950
Look,

04:33.240 --> 04:35.000
it's even in the newspaper.

04:35.400 --> 04:36.150
[From Stinky Bamboo Ditch to
Gold-Laden Land: Wasteland Yields Gold;]

04:35.510 --> 04:36.360
I always said it—

04:36.150 --> 04:36.909
[Qi Hang Property's Project Strikes Gold—
Golden Sands Pool Lives Up to Its Name]

04:36.390 --> 04:37.070
Xiaolan

04:37.070 --> 04:38.510
can pull off anything.

04:39.390 --> 04:40.390
They found gold

04:40.390 --> 04:41.430
on that plot?

04:43.630 --> 04:45.600
How does that even happen?

04:46.190 --> 04:47.650
This makes no difference.

04:47.920 --> 04:49.159
This might not be bad news

04:49.159 --> 04:50.159
for us, sir.

04:51.159 --> 04:52.240
The piece of land

04:52.800 --> 04:54.390
is next to our golf course.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.870
How did we not know about

04:55.870 --> 04:57.159
this spot before?

05:01.720 --> 05:02.630
I'm sorry,

05:02.870 --> 05:04.630
but I haven't received

05:04.650 --> 05:06.870
any instructions
regarding selling the land.

05:06.870 --> 05:08.680
Could you leave

05:09.160 --> 05:10.950
your contact details
if it would be convenient?

05:10.950 --> 05:12.600
And may I ask what your offer?

05:12.830 --> 05:14.720
I can pass it along to my boss.

05:15.720 --> 05:16.250
Alright.

05:16.750 --> 05:19.040
I'll get back to you if there are updates.

05:19.310 --> 05:19.840
Goodbye.

05:25.600 --> 05:26.000
You Li.

05:27.430 --> 05:27.950
Ms. Xia,

05:28.630 --> 05:29.390
several

05:29.390 --> 05:30.190
real estate companies

05:30.190 --> 05:30.800
have called asking

05:30.800 --> 05:32.360
if we're selling Golden Sands Pool.

05:32.360 --> 05:33.040
The highest offer

05:33.040 --> 05:34.370
has reached 12 million!

05:35.070 --> 05:35.870
The highest offer

05:35.870 --> 05:37.720
is from the American Wilson Group?

05:37.720 --> 05:38.040
Yes,

05:38.400 --> 05:39.159
the developer

05:39.159 --> 05:40.480
of the golf course.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.600
Okay, let's go with them.

05:42.600 --> 05:43.730
Contact them for me.

05:44.310 --> 05:46.190
Are we really going to sell that plot?

05:46.190 --> 05:47.159
Of course not.

05:47.830 --> 05:48.720
That's the great place our Ms. Xia

05:48.720 --> 05:50.240
spotted at first glance.

05:51.000 --> 05:52.030
Our Ms. Xia

05:52.240 --> 05:53.950
is a businessperson with vision—

05:53.950 --> 05:54.870
she wants to build buildings,

05:54.870 --> 05:56.310
not flip land for a quick profit.

05:56.310 --> 05:57.970
How could she just turn around

05:58.360 --> 05:59.560
and sell it for a markup?

05:59.560 --> 06:00.580
Our Attorney Zhou is

06:00.580 --> 06:02.930
really perceptive about people.

06:03.950 --> 06:05.720
Then why do you want to meet

06:05.800 --> 06:06.830
with that American businessman?

06:06.830 --> 06:07.960
You'll know in time.

06:08.480 --> 06:09.140
Zhou Cheng,

06:09.360 --> 06:11.430
have I been moving

06:11.430 --> 06:12.390
too fast lately?

06:13.950 --> 06:14.750
Yes, too fast.

06:15.270 --> 06:16.800
So fast you're about to fly.

06:18.920 --> 06:19.480
Ms. Xia,

06:19.740 --> 06:20.530
we heard gold

06:20.560 --> 06:21.800
was discovered here.

06:21.830 --> 06:23.560
What are your thoughts on this?

06:23.830 --> 06:24.190
Yes.

06:24.480 --> 06:25.630
We'll let the Futian Subdistrict Office

06:25.630 --> 06:27.430
keep the gold we found for now.

06:28.000 --> 06:29.560
As for the construction site...

06:29.560 --> 06:30.920
we'll suspend work temporarily

06:30.920 --> 06:32.240
and invite the geological survey team

06:32.240 --> 06:33.040
to come and determine

06:33.040 --> 06:35.440
whether there's actually a gold mine here.

06:35.750 --> 06:36.920
I'd bet anything

06:37.870 --> 06:38.510
that you buried

06:38.510 --> 06:39.950
that gold yourself.

06:41.560 --> 06:43.190
Xia Xiaolan, oh Xia Xiaolan.

06:43.190 --> 06:44.159
Did you know beforehand

06:44.159 --> 06:45.360
that there was gold here?

06:45.360 --> 06:47.040
You're still so full of schemes.

06:47.040 --> 06:47.600
No.

06:48.040 --> 06:49.630
Although I'd heard

06:49.630 --> 06:51.360
the legend of "gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground,"

06:51.360 --> 06:52.360
I chose this name

06:52.360 --> 06:53.560
purely for good luck.

06:53.600 --> 06:54.950
I never imagined it would actually happen.

06:54.950 --> 06:55.920
Xia Xiaolan,

06:56.560 --> 06:57.120
just how many tricks

06:57.120 --> 06:58.580
do you have up your sleeve?

06:59.480 --> 07:00.870
Good thing I was smart enough

07:00.870 --> 07:02.030
to choose to partner with you

07:02.030 --> 07:03.520
rather than against you.

07:04.430 --> 07:04.990
Cheers.

07:16.390 --> 07:18.000
Alright, I'll call you when I need you.

07:18.000 --> 07:18.750
Okay, Mr. Ge.

07:19.920 --> 07:20.270
Ms. Xia.

07:20.270 --> 07:21.070
Are things ready

07:21.070 --> 07:22.390
with Uncle and Director Pan?

07:22.390 --> 07:24.070
Uncle arranged a meeting
with Director Pan long ago.

07:24.070 --> 07:25.360
They are in the private room next door.

07:25.360 --> 07:25.750
Okay.

07:29.510 --> 07:30.160
Ms. Xia,

07:30.920 --> 07:34.270
you're even more stunning in real life
than on TV.

07:35.000 --> 07:36.920
You must be Mr. Wilson.

07:38.190 --> 07:39.830
I've heard that Americans

07:39.920 --> 07:41.830
are good at complimenting women.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.680
It is so nice to

07:43.700 --> 07:44.780
hear it today.

07:45.070 --> 07:47.070
I did not realize your English

07:47.070 --> 07:48.430
is so fluent, Ms. Xia.

07:48.750 --> 07:49.510
Thank you.

07:49.920 --> 07:51.520
But I'm afraid that flattery

07:51.720 --> 07:53.920
won't get you a discount

07:53.950 --> 07:55.880
on Jinshachi (Golden Sands Pool).

07:56.240 --> 07:57.360
Beautiful and witty.

07:57.360 --> 07:57.820
Please.

07:59.159 --> 08:00.890
Well, it's an honor to meet you.

08:07.360 --> 08:07.820
Cheers.

08:07.920 --> 08:08.430
Cheers.

08:13.600 --> 08:14.160
Ms. Xia,

08:14.750 --> 08:20.630
business... It naturally has
a big element of luck.

08:21.390 --> 08:23.600
And you seem to have plenty of it.

08:24.190 --> 08:25.560
You're buying

08:26.040 --> 08:26.950
that plot of land

08:26.950 --> 08:28.270
that conveniently runs next to

08:28.270 --> 08:29.390
my golf course.

08:30.360 --> 08:32.840
Somewhat of the convenience
when you think.

08:34.030 --> 08:35.390
Are you implying

08:35.390 --> 08:36.440
that I've been riding the coattails of

08:36.440 --> 08:38.169
your golf course development?

08:38.600 --> 08:41.360
Let's not dwell on history.
Now, we're here.

08:43.640 --> 08:44.670
Look, even if you did buy

08:44.670 --> 08:46.120
that plot of land just to

08:46.120 --> 08:47.510
flip it for a high price,

08:47.580 --> 08:48.440
I would say that you're

08:48.440 --> 08:50.390
a very smart businesswoman.

08:50.550 --> 08:53.980
I wouldn't mind that.
It's just three acres, more or less.

08:54.240 --> 08:55.030
If I

08:56.080 --> 08:59.120
buy it for 12 million dollars...

09:00.320 --> 09:01.320
it's not much of a challenge

09:01.320 --> 09:02.520
for the Wilson Group.

09:03.630 --> 09:04.720
So you're saying

09:04.720 --> 09:05.670
I bought that land

09:05.670 --> 09:07.890
specifically to squeeze money out of you?

09:07.890 --> 09:09.690
Then should I thank you

09:09.720 --> 09:10.750
for your generosity

09:10.750 --> 09:11.840
and leniency?

09:14.150 --> 09:15.910
How do you say it in Chinese?

09:17.000 --> 09:20.680
"Duh leh pyen-ee hi my guy"
(cashing in and pretending not to notice).

09:20.680 --> 09:22.450
I know exactly what you paid

09:22.480 --> 09:23.680
for that plot of land.

09:23.830 --> 09:24.600
Wedge between

09:24.600 --> 09:25.480
the golf course

09:25.740 --> 09:27.220
and the resort.

09:27.630 --> 09:28.240
Selling it to me

09:28.240 --> 09:29.370
is your best option.

09:29.800 --> 09:30.930
But if I...

09:31.030 --> 09:32.840
Hello, everybody!

09:34.910 --> 09:36.170
Having a big meal here?

09:36.680 --> 09:37.940
Talking big business?

09:38.510 --> 09:39.750
Sorry, I'm late.

09:40.000 --> 09:41.800
I'll punish myself with a drink.

09:42.550 --> 09:43.790
Let me drink one as an apology.

09:43.790 --> 09:44.740
Ms. Xia, who is this?

09:44.740 --> 09:45.740
Hold on, hold on!

09:46.000 --> 09:46.930
Hold on a minute.

09:49.600 --> 09:50.120
Look.

09:50.510 --> 09:52.240
This has nothing to do with her.

09:52.290 --> 09:53.550
I came of my own accord.

09:53.630 --> 09:54.630
Because if not,

09:55.240 --> 09:57.550
you would've gotten
Jinshachi (Golden Sands Pool).

09:57.550 --> 09:58.950
Let me introduce myself.

09:59.080 --> 10:00.940
I'm Mr. Du, from Chengrong Group.

10:02.270 --> 10:03.270
So, Mr. Wilson,

10:03.750 --> 10:06.600
I heard that you offered 12 million?

10:10.600 --> 10:13.630
I'm gonna offer 18 million!

10:14.550 --> 10:15.880
In Chinese, we call that

10:16.150 --> 10:17.200
18 million—

10:17.440 --> 10:18.600
"sure to prosper!"

10:19.240 --> 10:20.440
How about it, Ms. Xia?

10:20.600 --> 10:21.660
If you are willing,

10:21.720 --> 10:23.240
we can sign the contract right now.

10:23.240 --> 10:23.720
Hua.

10:26.320 --> 10:26.980
Du Zhaohui,

10:27.000 --> 10:27.860
that's enough.

10:29.670 --> 10:30.510
Ms. Xia,

10:31.030 --> 10:33.150
if you weren't happy with my offer,

10:33.150 --> 10:35.720
we might've continued to negotiate.

10:36.240 --> 10:37.100
But this kind of

10:37.510 --> 10:40.030
last-minute price adjustment...

10:40.270 --> 10:42.240
That's extremely disrespectful.

10:42.330 --> 10:43.960
We've got nothing more to talk about here.

10:43.960 --> 10:44.840
Mr. Wilson!

10:45.870 --> 10:46.390
Goodbye!

10:46.390 --> 10:47.280
Have a good day!

10:47.360 --> 10:47.720
Bye-bye.

10:47.720 --> 10:48.920
Ge Jian, see them out.

10:51.910 --> 10:52.640
How was that?

10:53.720 --> 10:55.320
I put on a good show, didn't I?

10:56.120 --> 10:57.050
Why are you here?

10:57.080 --> 10:58.440
To help you drive up the price.

10:58.440 --> 11:00.030
Didn't I pull that off flawlessly?

11:00.030 --> 11:01.090
Drive up the price?

11:01.150 --> 11:02.550
You drove the buyer away.

11:03.150 --> 11:04.150
Let him go.

11:05.000 --> 11:06.960
It's not like
you were really going to sell to him.

11:06.960 --> 11:08.110
Knowing you as I do,

11:08.670 --> 11:09.200
I suppose

11:09.200 --> 11:10.510
the real buyer is...

11:22.240 --> 11:23.040
Director Pan,

11:23.150 --> 11:23.720
you see,

11:24.320 --> 11:26.520
that's basically the whole situation.

11:27.470 --> 11:27.860
Okay.

11:28.200 --> 11:29.360
I won't say much else.

11:29.360 --> 11:31.510
Let me go back and think about it.

11:31.750 --> 11:34.080
No matter how much we hype up
Golden Sands Pool,

11:34.080 --> 11:36.270
it's all pointless
if we can't convince the bank.

11:36.270 --> 11:37.440
It's useless for us to claim

11:37.440 --> 11:38.870
Golden Sands Pool is worth 10 million.

11:38.870 --> 11:39.600
We have to make the person

11:39.600 --> 11:41.750
responsible for loans at the bank
believe it.

11:41.750 --> 11:42.750
So, on the day I meet

11:42.750 --> 11:43.550
with Harold,

11:43.960 --> 11:44.720
Uncle, you'll handle the negotiations

11:44.720 --> 11:46.270
with the loan officers.

11:46.910 --> 11:47.640
Understood.

11:48.460 --> 11:49.600
I'll arrange a meeting later with

11:49.600 --> 11:50.630
Director Pan from the bank.

11:50.630 --> 11:52.400
Let's not talk about work today.

11:52.400 --> 11:53.390
Just the two of us brothers,

11:53.390 --> 11:54.240
let's drink till we drop.

11:54.240 --> 11:54.770
Alright!

11:54.790 --> 11:55.120
Come on, cheers!

11:55.120 --> 11:56.080
Come on, drink!

11:56.360 --> 11:56.820
Cheers!

11:56.960 --> 11:57.420
Come on!

12:01.480 --> 12:02.280
You downed it!

12:02.550 --> 12:03.960
Don't act like you know everything.

12:03.960 --> 12:04.420
I'm off.

12:04.870 --> 12:05.910
Did I guess wrong?

12:07.320 --> 12:07.870
No way.

12:08.080 --> 12:09.510
We're business partners now, right?

12:09.510 --> 12:11.360
Knowing you as I do...

12:13.240 --> 12:14.320
I guessed right, didn't I?

12:14.320 --> 12:15.120
I knew it.

12:16.030 --> 12:18.890
You really don't have anything else
to see me about?

12:19.270 --> 12:19.960
I do.

12:20.510 --> 12:21.480
Didn't you ask me before

12:21.480 --> 12:23.940
to help track down
the Yu family's antiques?

12:24.360 --> 12:25.360
I recently found a clue

12:25.360 --> 12:27.120
about that blue-and-white porcelain vase.

12:27.120 --> 12:28.120
Because it was brought to Gangdao

12:28.120 --> 12:28.920
from Shengcheng,

12:28.920 --> 12:30.200
it was relatively easy to trace.

12:30.200 --> 12:30.670
Really?

12:30.840 --> 12:31.770
So who has it now?

12:37.790 --> 12:39.120
You want shrimp, right?

12:39.150 --> 12:39.610
Come on.

12:40.080 --> 12:40.910
I'll peel it for you.

12:40.910 --> 12:41.310
Let me.

12:41.510 --> 12:42.440
No need, no need.

12:43.600 --> 12:45.240
I've already tracked it down.

12:45.240 --> 12:47.640
It's in the hands of someone
called Mr. Qiu.

12:47.720 --> 12:48.320
He's an antique dealer

12:48.320 --> 12:49.630
in Gangdao,

12:50.270 --> 12:50.910
and

12:51.150 --> 12:52.830
a lot of black-market antiques there

12:52.830 --> 12:53.870
go through him.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.910
I've managed to
make an appointment with him,

12:55.910 --> 12:57.710
but he's really hard to pin down.

12:58.270 --> 12:58.670
Okay.

12:59.140 --> 13:01.540
Then let me thank you
on behalf of Granny Yu.

13:01.840 --> 13:02.900
No need to thank me.

13:03.550 --> 13:04.870
We're...

13:07.870 --> 13:08.910
business partners.

13:08.910 --> 13:10.370
Remember that, partners.

13:10.440 --> 13:10.900
I'm off.

13:17.020 --> 13:18.730
[Qi Hang Property]

13:26.790 --> 13:28.840
So, did they approve it or not?

13:29.200 --> 13:30.360
Should we just call Xiaolan

13:30.360 --> 13:31.440
on her cell phone and ask?

13:31.440 --> 13:33.900
Sit down.
Pacing around isn't going to help.

13:35.730 --> 13:36.210
Mr. Mao,

13:36.240 --> 13:37.200
how about we eat first?

13:37.200 --> 13:38.150
The dishes are getting cold.

13:38.150 --> 13:39.840
Okay, let's eat while we wait.

13:39.860 --> 13:40.320
Come on.

13:45.240 --> 13:45.770
How is it?

13:46.600 --> 13:47.930
Did the bank approve it?

13:51.480 --> 13:52.810
They didn't approve it?

13:57.030 --> 13:58.600
Say something.

13:58.630 --> 13:59.760
Did they approve it?

14:03.510 --> 14:04.080
The loan got approved!

14:04.080 --> 14:05.740
We have the money to build now!

14:07.360 --> 14:08.080
Great!

14:08.600 --> 14:09.390
Wait, wait!

14:09.670 --> 14:11.120
How much did they approve?

14:11.120 --> 14:11.650
How much?

14:12.750 --> 14:15.240
Fifteen million!

14:15.840 --> 14:17.270
Oh my God.

14:17.290 --> 14:18.550
Less than three million

14:18.550 --> 14:20.680
turned into five times that in a month!

14:20.790 --> 14:21.630
I didn't expect

14:21.630 --> 14:22.790
they'd actually give us

14:22.790 --> 14:23.850
15 million either.

14:24.200 --> 14:25.240
Speaking of which,

14:25.240 --> 14:26.770
we have to thank Du Zhaohui.

14:27.270 --> 14:28.120
Let's raise a toast in Du Zhaohui's honor!

14:28.120 --> 14:28.600
Come on.

14:29.030 --> 14:29.480
Ms. Xia.

14:29.480 --> 14:31.030
Let's wish for good luck.

14:31.440 --> 14:33.770
Qi Hang, Qi Hang,
brave the wind and waves!

14:33.840 --> 14:35.480
-Let's shout the slogan.
-One, two, three!

14:35.480 --> 14:38.670
Qi Hang, Qi Hang,
brave the wind and waves!

14:38.690 --> 14:40.180
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

14:40.600 --> 14:41.870
What did the bank say?

14:43.030 --> 14:43.510
What?

14:44.600 --> 14:45.660
That's wonderful!

14:45.910 --> 14:46.440
Really?

14:46.910 --> 14:49.110
Okay, okay. I'll tell the Young Master.

14:50.320 --> 14:51.320
Young Master! Young Master!

14:51.320 --> 14:52.520
Good news! Good news!

14:52.600 --> 14:53.480
Ms. Xia's loan

14:53.480 --> 14:54.540
has been approved.

14:55.030 --> 14:55.830
That's great!

14:56.390 --> 14:57.320
Where is she now?

14:57.360 --> 14:59.560
She's celebrating at Qi Hang right now.

14:59.960 --> 15:00.950
She didn't invite me?

15:00.950 --> 15:07.060
♪ Love has faded,
and so has the bond between us ♪

15:03.630 --> 15:04.230
Forget it.

15:04.550 --> 15:06.360
That Jerk Zhou is definitely there—

15:06.360 --> 15:07.300
I don't want to see him anyway.

15:07.300 --> 15:12.810
♪ Yet, why do I still love you? ♪

15:09.200 --> 15:09.840
You two,

15:10.360 --> 15:11.020
get to work!

15:11.080 --> 15:12.280
Or I'll dock your pay.

15:13.000 --> 15:14.720
You've got to admit, I'm awesome, right?

15:14.720 --> 15:16.440
Awesome. You're the best.

15:16.840 --> 15:17.320
From the very first day

15:17.320 --> 15:18.390
I met you,

15:18.390 --> 15:19.720
I knew you could make it.

15:20.150 --> 15:21.390
Put me down already.

15:22.960 --> 15:23.760
Stand steady.

15:25.910 --> 15:27.000
I think so too.

15:28.150 --> 15:29.280
Alright, go inside.

15:29.600 --> 15:30.440
Or Granny Yu

15:30.440 --> 15:32.100
will suddenly come out again.

15:33.000 --> 15:33.720
Um...

15:34.390 --> 15:37.030
Jiang Yan will be discharged
in a couple of days.

15:37.030 --> 15:37.750
Really?

15:38.320 --> 15:39.120
That's great.

15:39.360 --> 15:40.200
How is her recovery?

15:40.200 --> 15:41.750
Does she still need follow-up checks?

15:41.750 --> 15:42.720
She'll probably still need

15:42.720 --> 15:43.850
regular check-ups.

15:44.270 --> 15:46.600
But her daily life shouldn't be a problem.

15:47.550 --> 15:49.150
Every time I think of

15:49.510 --> 15:50.570
what Jiang Yan has endured,

15:50.570 --> 15:52.300
I feel both sorry and grateful.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.810
She's a good person

15:54.030 --> 15:55.560
and an upright prosecutor.

15:57.030 --> 15:58.030
She truly

15:58.320 --> 16:01.050
deserves someone
who loves her wholeheartedly.

16:01.240 --> 16:01.670
Oh,

16:01.790 --> 16:04.840
she said after she's discharged,

16:05.510 --> 16:06.840
she wants to have a meal with both of us.

16:06.840 --> 16:07.750
Is that okay?

16:08.030 --> 16:08.750
Of course.

16:10.440 --> 16:12.170
Okay, you should head back now.

16:12.200 --> 16:13.240
I'll watch you go in.

16:13.240 --> 16:14.030
What's there to see?

16:14.030 --> 16:15.030
You see it every day. Go.

16:15.030 --> 16:17.670
-What if something happens to you?
-Go already!

16:17.670 --> 16:18.200
Bye-bye!

16:19.240 --> 16:19.700
I'm off.

16:31.670 --> 16:32.270
Granny Yu.

16:33.000 --> 16:35.000
It's so late. Aren't you asleep yet?

16:35.720 --> 16:36.240
Not yet.

16:37.910 --> 16:38.960
If I were asleep,

16:39.270 --> 16:40.360
how could I have heard

16:40.360 --> 16:42.560
you two talking about me behind my back?

16:43.910 --> 16:45.200
You young people

16:45.480 --> 16:46.750
always think

16:47.270 --> 16:48.390
work is the most important thing,

16:48.390 --> 16:49.790
that a career comes above all else.

16:49.790 --> 16:50.590
But honestly,

16:51.080 --> 16:52.630
when you reach my age,

16:52.840 --> 16:54.080
you'll understand

16:54.720 --> 16:56.520
that the most important thing is

16:57.270 --> 16:59.070
keeping the people close to you.

17:00.510 --> 17:01.630
I'll stop rambling now,

17:01.630 --> 17:03.910
or I'll just annoy you.

17:04.640 --> 17:05.900
Goodnight, Granny Yu.

17:06.109 --> 17:06.770
Goodnight!

17:09.349 --> 17:10.550
I want to keep him too.

17:11.069 --> 17:12.109
There are still too many things

17:12.109 --> 17:13.240
I haven't finished.

17:14.200 --> 17:15.720
I hope the day I wake from this dream

17:15.720 --> 17:16.920
comes a little later—

17:17.000 --> 17:18.130
just a little later.

17:18.480 --> 17:20.680
I want to see Liu Fen find happiness.

17:21.200 --> 17:23.400
I want to help Granny Yu find her family.

17:23.640 --> 17:25.520
I also want to see
the Golden Sands Pool project completed,

17:25.520 --> 17:28.000
even if only in the dream.

17:32.270 --> 17:32.730
Ms. Xia.

17:32.880 --> 17:33.480
Mr. Mao.

17:34.070 --> 17:35.720
The terrain of this lake is quite complex.

17:35.720 --> 17:37.240
We've cleared the surrounding weeds

17:37.240 --> 17:38.510
and silt.

17:38.830 --> 17:40.490
We're ready for the next plan.

17:41.070 --> 17:42.790
If we build,
we must build high-quality buildings.

17:42.790 --> 17:44.270
Otherwise, it would be a disservice

17:44.270 --> 17:45.880
to Golden Sands Pool's current fame.

17:45.880 --> 17:47.200
I imagine the buyers who come

17:47.200 --> 17:48.880
attracted by the legend of
this gold-bearing land

17:48.880 --> 17:50.440
wouldn't want to see

17:50.460 --> 17:51.240
just an ordinary concrete block

17:51.240 --> 17:52.270
going up here.

17:52.590 --> 17:53.070
Ms. Xia,

17:53.510 --> 17:55.160
the Golden Sands Pool is quite large.

17:55.160 --> 17:57.090
We'd lose space for so many houses.

17:59.110 --> 18:00.330
The pool must be preserved,

18:00.330 --> 18:02.130
but we must shrink the area

18:02.160 --> 18:03.510
to about one mu.

18:04.030 --> 18:06.440
In the center,
we'll build a courtyard landscape.

18:06.440 --> 18:07.160
That way,

18:07.510 --> 18:09.270
on the left, you have the golf course;

18:09.270 --> 18:11.200
on the right, Qingyue Lake;

18:11.480 --> 18:13.740
and in the middle, the courtyard garden.

18:13.790 --> 18:15.400
No matter which angle you look from,

18:15.400 --> 18:16.790
the scenery will be excellent—

18:16.790 --> 18:17.720
very appealing.

18:18.070 --> 18:19.920
Yes, we sacrifice some floor area,

18:19.920 --> 18:20.790
but in return, we get

18:20.790 --> 18:22.920
the best possible living experience.

18:24.240 --> 18:26.110
Sounds like
you've genuinely planned this out.

18:26.110 --> 18:27.110
I thought

18:27.110 --> 18:29.110
you were so focused on being the boss

18:29.110 --> 18:30.160
that you'd dump the architectural design

18:30.160 --> 18:31.310
on someone else.

18:32.000 --> 18:33.720
Mr. Mao, you're joking.

18:33.750 --> 18:35.400
My fellow classmates and peers

18:35.400 --> 18:37.200
have spent their entire careers
drawing blueprints,

18:37.200 --> 18:38.350
but very few ever see

18:38.350 --> 18:40.240
their designs become real buildings.

18:40.240 --> 18:41.920
I run my own company now.
If I don't do the design myself,

18:41.920 --> 18:43.310
am I really supposed to wait

18:43.310 --> 18:44.480
for someone else to hire

18:44.480 --> 18:45.410
a rookie like me?

18:45.550 --> 18:46.240
Besides,

18:46.510 --> 18:47.960
I wouldn't want to miss the opportunity

18:47.960 --> 18:49.110
to have a mentor

18:49.110 --> 18:50.510
as good as you guiding me.

18:51.090 --> 18:52.130
Y-You girl...

18:52.510 --> 18:54.710
you're getting smooth with your words.

19:04.110 --> 19:04.830
Great.

19:05.200 --> 19:06.920
At least you haven't forgotten

19:06.920 --> 19:07.440
that your true calling

19:07.440 --> 19:09.000
is architectural design.

19:09.480 --> 19:10.110
Xiaolan,

19:10.640 --> 19:12.240
I have something to tell you.

19:12.310 --> 19:14.200
I've recommended you

19:14.200 --> 19:15.640
for the Jiangcheng Architecture Symposium

19:15.640 --> 19:17.970
based on your design for the Haihua Hotel.

19:18.360 --> 19:19.070
When you're there,

19:19.070 --> 19:20.310
you must seize the opportunity

19:20.310 --> 19:21.880
to network with your peers.

19:22.350 --> 19:23.350
While we're at it,

19:23.510 --> 19:25.480
I'll take you to make your debut—

19:26.590 --> 19:27.590
let everyone see you,

19:27.590 --> 19:28.790
my new apprentice.

19:29.350 --> 19:29.750
Okay.

19:30.000 --> 19:31.060
Thank you, Mr. Mao.

19:31.440 --> 19:33.300
I've already thought it through.

19:33.310 --> 19:34.960
We're going to build

19:34.960 --> 19:36.720
a building with one elevator
shared between two units,

19:36.720 --> 19:37.920
five floors in total.

19:38.000 --> 19:40.070
Each first-floor unit comes with a garage

19:40.070 --> 19:41.200
in the basement.

19:41.510 --> 19:42.110
As for the top floor,

19:42.110 --> 19:43.570
we'll build a roof garden.

19:43.590 --> 19:44.350
The floors below the top

19:44.350 --> 19:45.680
will be standard units,

19:45.880 --> 19:46.550
and the top floor can

19:46.550 --> 19:47.810
also have a small loft,

19:47.880 --> 19:49.640
making it a duplex penthouse.

19:50.920 --> 19:51.920
If we do this,

19:52.110 --> 19:53.750
we'll be building many fewer units.

19:53.750 --> 19:54.960
Can we really make money?

19:54.960 --> 19:56.350
Whether it's profitable

19:56.350 --> 19:57.440
depends on

19:57.440 --> 19:59.170
what price we sell the units at.

19:59.210 --> 20:01.070
I think Xiaolan's overall vision

20:01.070 --> 20:02.070
is very clear.

20:02.440 --> 20:02.970
Xiaolan,

20:03.240 --> 20:04.200
go ahead boldly.

20:04.830 --> 20:05.200
Okay.

20:05.440 --> 20:06.640
I'll draw the designs

20:06.640 --> 20:07.310
and show you.

20:07.310 --> 20:07.970
Okay, okay.

20:08.030 --> 20:09.560
Man, this is a construction site!

20:09.560 --> 20:10.880
You can't come in without permission!

20:10.880 --> 20:12.140
Don't come here again!

20:12.240 --> 20:12.830
Don't come back!

20:12.830 --> 20:14.070
Look how dangerous this is!

20:14.070 --> 20:15.000
Go back! Go back!

20:15.110 --> 20:16.040
Don't come back!

20:16.400 --> 20:17.330
Go back, go back.

20:17.440 --> 20:18.680
Break it up. Go back, everyone.

20:18.680 --> 20:19.160
Go back.

20:19.920 --> 20:20.920
What are you doing?

20:20.920 --> 20:21.270
Stop!

20:21.270 --> 20:22.200
Okay, okay.

20:22.350 --> 20:23.480
Stop playing! Stop!

20:23.640 --> 20:24.310
Officer,

20:24.590 --> 20:25.540
we're not here to cause trouble.

20:25.540 --> 20:26.110
You see,

20:26.110 --> 20:27.480
gold was found here, wasn't it?

20:27.480 --> 20:28.480
My grandpa is old.

20:28.510 --> 20:29.350
When he heard the news,

20:29.350 --> 20:30.270
he couldn't take the shock

20:30.270 --> 20:31.310
and collapsed right then.

20:31.310 --> 20:32.350
Look at his condition—

20:32.350 --> 20:33.720
he's getting worse day by day.

20:33.720 --> 20:34.480
He just wants to go in

20:34.480 --> 20:35.590
and take one last look.

20:35.590 --> 20:37.510
Otherwise, he won't rest in peace.

20:37.510 --> 20:38.170
Who are you?

20:38.730 --> 20:39.730
I'm his grandson.

20:41.010 --> 20:41.920
This is their construction site.

20:41.920 --> 20:43.240
They have every right to develop it.

20:43.240 --> 20:44.240
You show up here every day
with all these people...

20:44.240 --> 20:44.880
Mr. Ge Jian,

20:44.880 --> 20:45.550
Ms. Xia is looking for you.

20:45.550 --> 20:46.640
You should be grateful they didn't

20:46.640 --> 20:47.480
hold you responsible.

20:47.480 --> 20:48.240
Disperse now.

20:48.240 --> 20:49.530
Take your people and go back.

20:49.530 --> 20:50.680
We're not causing any trouble.

20:50.680 --> 20:52.000
And we won't get in the way
of her digging for gold.

20:52.000 --> 20:53.600
We just want to go in and look.

20:58.000 --> 20:58.480
Ms. Xia.

20:59.070 --> 21:00.200
You wanted to see me?

21:01.160 --> 21:02.760
The Luo family is here again?

21:03.550 --> 21:04.790
These past few days, that Luo guy

21:04.790 --> 21:06.000
has been coming every day,

21:06.000 --> 21:07.030
insisting on seeing you.

21:07.030 --> 21:07.880
Today, knowing you're here,

21:07.880 --> 21:08.640
he even

21:08.640 --> 21:10.070
had his grandfather carried over,

21:10.070 --> 21:12.000
worried that you wouldn't show up.

21:12.650 --> 21:14.170
He sees the dump

21:14.200 --> 21:15.440
has turned into a treasure land

21:15.440 --> 21:16.440
and wants in on it.

21:17.070 --> 21:18.550
Tell him to have the others leave,

21:18.550 --> 21:19.880
and I'll agree to meet him and his family.

21:19.880 --> 21:20.240
Okay.

21:36.110 --> 21:37.030
Easy, easy.

21:40.750 --> 21:42.210
Former Village Chief Luo,

21:42.480 --> 21:43.860
I only agreed to see you

21:44.160 --> 21:44.720
out of respect

21:44.720 --> 21:46.030
for your age.

21:46.550 --> 21:48.510
Don't bring up
anything about land rights with me.

21:48.510 --> 21:50.720
I bought this plot legally and properly.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.790
You know perfectly well yourself

21:51.790 --> 21:53.720
whether you're in the right or not.

21:53.830 --> 21:55.270
Fine, fine.

21:56.000 --> 21:57.750
You've got guts, young lady.

21:58.510 --> 21:59.830
You stole my family's

21:59.830 --> 22:01.200
feng shui treasure land.

22:01.200 --> 22:02.600
We can't just let this go.

22:03.000 --> 22:04.460
You have to compensate us.

22:05.350 --> 22:06.880
I don't owe your family anything.

22:06.880 --> 22:08.480
Why should I compensate you?

22:08.590 --> 22:10.390
Or are you trying to threaten me?

22:10.440 --> 22:11.720
That won't work on me.

22:12.480 --> 22:14.270
You can ask your grandson
if you don't believe me.

22:14.270 --> 22:14.750
Fine.

22:15.510 --> 22:17.370
Since you mentioned my grandson,

22:17.450 --> 22:18.440
then arrange a job for him

22:18.440 --> 22:19.590
at your company.

22:20.350 --> 22:21.920
Make him a manager or something.

22:21.920 --> 22:23.650
Manager is out of the question.

22:23.720 --> 22:25.480
But I'm still hiring security guards.

22:25.480 --> 22:26.210
Want the job?

22:27.030 --> 22:28.750
You're making Yaozong a security guard?

22:28.750 --> 22:30.110
You're looking down on us too much!

22:30.110 --> 22:30.720
Yeah!

22:31.000 --> 22:32.000
Yaozong is the only male heir

22:32.000 --> 22:32.790
of the Luo family for three generations!

22:32.790 --> 22:34.640
How can you run things this way,
little girl?

22:34.640 --> 22:35.070
Fine.

22:35.670 --> 22:36.440
Think it over and come back

22:36.440 --> 22:37.900
to me when you've decided.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.440
Wait, wait, wait!

22:43.640 --> 22:45.790
There's no justice in this world!

22:46.400 --> 22:47.310
Our Luo family

22:47.310 --> 22:49.070
has done good deeds all our lives,

22:49.070 --> 22:51.270
but how did we end up like this?

22:52.070 --> 22:53.750
We treated Golden Sands Pool

22:53.750 --> 22:54.810
as a treasure land,

22:55.030 --> 22:55.920
not because of

22:55.920 --> 22:57.200
any gold here.

22:58.750 --> 22:59.790
Over 20 years ago,

22:59.790 --> 23:01.160
I saved someone here.

23:01.630 --> 23:02.830
That's the true source

23:02.830 --> 23:04.290
of our family's blessing.

23:04.920 --> 23:06.120
When did that happen?

23:06.510 --> 23:08.240
That was over 20 years ago.

23:09.830 --> 23:11.240
I remember one night...

23:11.590 --> 23:16.880
I, the old servant, was in a rush.

23:17.790 --> 23:19.750
I stepped forward

23:20.030 --> 23:22.200
and knelt down quickly.

23:34.920 --> 23:37.520
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground!

23:37.590 --> 23:40.190
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground!

23:57.030 --> 23:57.960
You're in luck.

23:58.720 --> 23:59.550
Fortunately,

24:00.270 --> 24:01.400
it's me you ran into.

24:03.070 --> 24:05.160
That person stayed at our home
for a couple of days,

24:05.160 --> 24:06.560
then left without a word.

24:07.200 --> 24:09.070
About half a year later,

24:10.000 --> 24:11.400
someone left a wooden box

24:11.720 --> 24:12.790
at our house.

24:13.240 --> 24:14.170
When I opened it,

24:14.270 --> 24:16.070
there was an antique porcelain vase

24:16.070 --> 24:17.200
along with a letter.

24:17.590 --> 24:19.400
The letter was signed

24:20.110 --> 24:21.310
by a man surnamed Qiu.

24:21.920 --> 24:22.550
Qiu...

24:22.960 --> 24:24.070
I've already tracked it down.

24:24.070 --> 24:25.760
It's in the hands of someone
called Mr. Qiu.

24:25.760 --> 24:26.350
He's an antique dealer

24:26.350 --> 24:27.240
in Gangdao,

24:28.160 --> 24:29.750
and a lot of black-market antiques there

24:29.750 --> 24:30.720
go through him.

24:31.590 --> 24:32.550
An antique vase?

24:33.880 --> 24:35.440
Could it really be that coincidental?

24:35.440 --> 24:36.440
Do you remember

24:36.860 --> 24:38.190
how old

24:38.310 --> 24:39.200
that man was?

24:39.590 --> 24:40.720
What he looked like?

24:40.880 --> 24:42.940
Where are the vase and the letter now?

24:46.030 --> 24:46.890
I feel dizzy...

24:47.960 --> 24:48.820
I feel dizzy...

24:49.200 --> 24:50.730
I can't remember right now.

24:51.230 --> 24:51.830
Unless...

24:51.880 --> 24:53.400
Unless you make my grandson

24:53.400 --> 24:54.000
a manager.

24:55.640 --> 24:56.440
Listen up,

24:57.110 --> 24:58.960
I can be persuaded but not threatened.

24:58.960 --> 25:00.750
Luo Yaozong can only be a security guard.

25:00.750 --> 25:01.580
Take it or leave it.

25:01.580 --> 25:02.790
If he doesn't want it, forget it.

25:02.790 --> 25:03.310
That piece of information

25:03.310 --> 25:05.000
is valuable to me now,

25:05.360 --> 25:07.920
but that doesn't mean
it will still be valuable in a few days.

25:07.920 --> 25:08.750
From what I can see,

25:08.750 --> 25:09.350
Gancun Village isn't exactly a place

25:09.350 --> 25:10.610
that can hide secrets.

25:11.000 --> 25:13.060
It shouldn't be hard to investigate.

25:13.920 --> 25:14.440
Fine.

25:16.110 --> 25:17.400
I've never seen

25:17.400 --> 25:18.730
a woman as brazen as you.

25:19.480 --> 25:21.280
I didn't say I wouldn't tell you.

25:21.510 --> 25:22.680
But you're not offering us

25:22.680 --> 25:23.810
anything in return.

25:24.350 --> 25:25.080
Is that fair?

25:25.480 --> 25:26.010
Grandpa,

25:26.310 --> 25:27.550
I don't want to be a security guard.

25:27.550 --> 25:28.510
What do you know?

25:30.240 --> 25:31.400
Have you made a decision?

25:31.400 --> 25:32.720
If you won't say it, I'm leaving.

25:32.720 --> 25:33.380
Wait, wait.

25:34.160 --> 25:35.220
Alright, alright.

25:36.240 --> 25:38.070
Yaozong will take the position.

25:39.240 --> 25:40.370
If he does a good job,

25:40.790 --> 25:42.000
he can be promoted to manager, right?

25:42.000 --> 25:42.600
Of course.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.200
As long as you work hard,

25:44.200 --> 25:46.240
everyone has a chance for promotion.

25:46.240 --> 25:47.440
It all depends on him.

25:48.880 --> 25:49.560
Alright then,

25:49.560 --> 25:50.360
I'll tell you.

25:51.600 --> 25:53.510
It was a blue-and-white porcelain vase.

25:53.510 --> 25:54.440
About this high,

25:55.400 --> 25:56.830
with an opening this wide.

25:56.830 --> 25:57.470
And the letter

25:57.470 --> 25:58.670
was tucked inside it.

25:58.880 --> 25:59.680
As for the man,

26:00.200 --> 26:02.260
he was probably in his mid-twenties.

26:02.460 --> 26:03.460
His height...

26:05.070 --> 26:06.830
was about the same as our Yaozong.

26:06.830 --> 26:08.750
He had a cut on his forehead at the time,

26:08.750 --> 26:09.160
so I

26:09.160 --> 26:11.110
didn't dare look at his face directly.

26:11.110 --> 26:12.920
Although his clothes were dirty,

26:12.920 --> 26:14.880
I could tell he came from
a well-off family.

26:14.880 --> 26:17.000
As for the letter,
I can't find it anymore.

26:17.000 --> 26:19.550
I remember he told me at the time

26:20.030 --> 26:21.690
that he ran into some enemies.

26:22.160 --> 26:23.720
Could he be Granny Yu's son?

26:24.550 --> 26:25.510
What exactly

26:25.510 --> 26:26.910
happened to him back then

26:27.200 --> 26:28.400
that caused such serious injuries?

26:28.400 --> 26:29.440
That's all

26:29.460 --> 26:30.260
I can tell you.

26:30.890 --> 26:32.620
I definitely didn't lie to you.

26:33.960 --> 26:34.920
Whether you lied or not,

26:34.920 --> 26:35.880
I'll find out.

26:36.830 --> 26:37.360
Alright.

26:37.750 --> 26:38.680
You start

26:38.680 --> 26:39.940
officially tomorrow.

26:40.110 --> 26:40.830
From now on, you're

26:40.830 --> 26:42.480
a security guard
at this construction site.

26:42.480 --> 26:44.060
If anyone causes trouble again,

26:44.060 --> 26:45.260
just drive them away.

26:47.160 --> 26:47.830
Mr. Luo,

26:48.430 --> 26:49.430
Ms. Xia has agreed

26:49.440 --> 26:50.680
to your request.

26:51.310 --> 26:52.880
Yaozong will come to work
at the site tomorrow.

26:52.880 --> 26:53.720
At your age,

26:53.720 --> 26:54.640
please don't make a fuss anymore.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.510
Come on, come on!

26:55.510 --> 26:57.240
Get on. Let them wheel you back.

26:59.070 --> 27:00.130
Careful, careful!

27:02.000 --> 27:02.440
Okay.

27:02.690 --> 27:03.220
Yaozong,

27:03.480 --> 27:04.240
since you're coming to work tomorrow,

27:04.240 --> 27:05.510
no more causing trouble!

27:05.510 --> 27:06.550
It's your job to keep an eye on them now.

27:06.550 --> 27:07.030
Go back!

27:14.830 --> 27:15.510
Look at

27:15.510 --> 27:16.320
this workplace of yours,

27:16.320 --> 27:18.600
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

27:16.640 --> 27:18.040
it's so small and shabby.

27:18.350 --> 27:20.210
It doesn't even look legitimate.

27:20.590 --> 27:21.590
You,

27:21.790 --> 27:23.160
a Huaqing Law School graduate,

27:23.160 --> 27:23.960
why did you join

27:23.960 --> 27:24.830
a private law firm

27:24.830 --> 27:25.750
like this?

27:26.320 --> 27:27.110
Think about it—

27:27.110 --> 27:28.400
if you could work at the procuratorate,

27:28.400 --> 27:29.190
how great would that be?

27:29.190 --> 27:30.680
You'd be in the same unit as my daughter.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.430
If you two get married in the future,

27:32.430 --> 27:33.400
wouldn't it be easier and faster

27:33.400 --> 27:34.350
to get an apartment allocated?

27:34.350 --> 27:35.230
You'll be a dual-income household!

27:35.230 --> 27:35.750
Auntie.

27:36.920 --> 27:37.880
You're an elder

27:37.880 --> 27:39.140
who watched me grow up.

27:39.560 --> 27:40.890
I respect you very much.

27:41.570 --> 27:43.370
But I hope you can respect me too.

27:43.400 --> 27:45.660
Jiang Yan and I are not in a relationship.

27:46.000 --> 27:47.480
I already have a girlfriend.

27:47.480 --> 27:49.790
You can't just go on like that
without considering others.

27:49.790 --> 27:51.000
As for my job

27:51.640 --> 27:52.570
and my future...

27:54.180 --> 27:55.980
you don't need to worry about it.

27:56.030 --> 27:57.520
How can you say that?

27:57.540 --> 27:58.130
I...

28:02.230 --> 28:03.930
[Xia Xiaolan paging: Meet me at Qi Hang.]

28:11.110 --> 28:11.570
Auntie.

28:12.640 --> 28:14.040
If there's nothing else,

28:15.070 --> 28:16.000
I'll see you out.

28:16.750 --> 28:17.160
You...

28:18.830 --> 28:20.630
Don't bother. I'll go by myself.

28:20.880 --> 28:22.340
I'll come again next time.

28:24.730 --> 28:28.690
[Qi Hang Property]

28:26.110 --> 28:26.680
So,

28:26.880 --> 28:28.880
I have to go to Gangdao immediately.

28:28.990 --> 28:30.110
But what Former Village Chief Luo said

28:30.110 --> 28:31.570
really sounds like a trap.

28:32.510 --> 28:34.510
I also think it's probably no coincidence

28:34.510 --> 28:36.590
that he suddenly brought up something

28:36.590 --> 28:38.160
from over 20 years ago today.

28:38.160 --> 28:39.760
But whether it's true or not,

28:39.790 --> 28:40.270
it's rare to have

28:40.270 --> 28:41.590
a lead about Granny Yu's family.

28:41.590 --> 28:42.510
I must go.

28:44.550 --> 28:44.920
Okay.

28:45.680 --> 28:46.940
I'll go with you, then.

28:47.030 --> 28:47.830
No, you can't.

28:48.190 --> 28:49.820
Weren't you suspecting this

28:49.880 --> 28:51.440
might be connected to that smuggling case?

28:51.440 --> 28:52.960
You and Jiang Yan just had that incident.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.560
If you show up in Gangdao now,

28:54.680 --> 28:55.790
wouldn't it be easier for those

28:55.790 --> 28:56.880
who want to hurt you to make a move?

28:56.880 --> 28:58.000
But I wanted to...

28:58.000 --> 28:58.830
Alright.

28:59.790 --> 29:00.520
Don't worry.

29:01.000 --> 29:02.790
Jiang Yan will be discharged soon.

29:02.790 --> 29:04.450
Stay and take good care of her first.

29:04.450 --> 29:05.440
I'll ask Du Zhaohui

29:05.440 --> 29:06.700
to handle my security.

29:06.880 --> 29:08.720
As a guest of the Du family in Gangdao,

29:08.720 --> 29:10.650
no one would dare to lay a hand on me.

29:11.880 --> 29:12.590
Once I get

29:12.590 --> 29:14.070
news about Granny Yu's family,

29:14.070 --> 29:15.470
I'll come straight back.

29:15.550 --> 29:16.070
Okay?

29:36.750 --> 29:37.150
Hello?

29:39.550 --> 29:40.350
I told her.

29:41.110 --> 29:43.170
I told her everything about the past.

29:45.840 --> 29:50.020
[Gangdao]

29:52.640 --> 29:53.510
Now that you're in Gangdao,

29:53.510 --> 29:54.720
you're on my turf.

29:55.110 --> 29:55.550
Relax.

29:55.790 --> 29:56.650
You'll be safe.

29:58.160 --> 30:00.510
Don't you think
that at a critical moment like this,

30:00.510 --> 30:01.400
I'm far more useful

30:01.400 --> 30:02.530
than that Jerk Zhou?

30:04.680 --> 30:05.640
Besides meeting Mr. Qiu,

30:05.640 --> 30:06.920
I need another favor.

30:07.960 --> 30:09.500
Help me find a property consultant

30:09.500 --> 30:11.110
to come check out Golden Sands Pool.

30:11.110 --> 30:12.350
It's also a good opportunity

30:12.350 --> 30:13.370
to let the Gangdao merchants
going to Shengcheng

30:13.370 --> 30:15.370
know about this gold-bearing land.

30:15.590 --> 30:16.350
I knew it.

30:16.830 --> 30:19.110
You came here
just to make money off our money.

30:19.110 --> 30:19.510
What?

30:20.160 --> 30:21.550
You Gangdao merchants are allowed

30:21.550 --> 30:22.750
to make money in Shengcheng,

30:22.750 --> 30:24.350
but we can't earn your money?

30:25.000 --> 30:25.830
Alright, alright.

30:25.830 --> 30:26.440
You win.

30:27.750 --> 30:28.680
Y-Young Master.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.160
There seems to be a car

30:30.160 --> 30:31.620
that's been following us.

30:36.890 --> 30:38.550
Young Master Du, didn't you say

30:38.550 --> 30:40.680
Gangdao was the safest place
with you around?

30:40.680 --> 30:41.310
Darn it.

30:42.160 --> 30:43.510
Who dares to tail me?

30:45.510 --> 30:46.110
Pull over.

31:04.070 --> 31:04.600
Let's go.

31:05.470 --> 31:05.920
Okay.

31:12.830 --> 31:13.960
They've spotted us.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.740
Did you get a good look?

31:16.550 --> 31:17.150
Yes, I did.

31:17.310 --> 31:17.840
It's her.

31:18.750 --> 31:19.160
Good.

31:19.700 --> 31:20.420
No need to follow anymore.

31:20.420 --> 31:21.680
-All done.
-Thank you.

31:22.550 --> 31:23.080
Let's go.

31:24.030 --> 31:24.510
Next.

31:24.750 --> 31:25.200
Mom?

31:25.680 --> 31:27.010
What are you doing here?

31:27.720 --> 31:29.270
What do you mean by that?

31:29.590 --> 31:30.550
Are you planning to

31:30.550 --> 31:32.480
leave the hospital just like that?

31:32.680 --> 31:33.550
Once my daughter is discharged,

31:33.550 --> 31:35.750
you think this whole thing is just over?

31:36.110 --> 31:36.590
Auntie,

31:37.310 --> 31:38.710
I never meant it that way.

31:39.000 --> 31:40.680
I won't ignore Jiang Yan's situation.

31:40.680 --> 31:42.160
But definitely not in the way

31:42.160 --> 31:43.240
you're thinking.

31:44.210 --> 31:45.200
Zhou Cheng, if that's your attitude,

31:45.200 --> 31:46.240
I'll go straight to your superiors,

31:46.240 --> 31:46.880
your parents,

31:46.880 --> 31:47.940
your whole family.

31:48.440 --> 31:49.070
If you feel

31:49.070 --> 31:50.440
you absolutely must do that,

31:50.440 --> 31:51.240
then go ahead.

31:51.830 --> 31:52.350
Do you think

31:52.350 --> 31:53.480
-I won't dare?
-Mom!

31:53.790 --> 31:54.920
Enough. Stop it.

31:55.680 --> 31:57.350
You're not making things hard
for Zhou Cheng—

31:57.350 --> 31:59.110
you're making things hard for me!

31:59.110 --> 32:00.570
Am I really that unworthy?

32:00.680 --> 32:01.350
Do I really need to use an accident

32:01.350 --> 32:02.790
to guilt-trip someone into being with me?

32:02.790 --> 32:04.030
What do you mean by "guilt-trip"?

32:04.030 --> 32:05.480
Am I not doing this for you?

32:05.480 --> 32:06.000
Think about it!

32:06.000 --> 32:06.720
Didn't you get

32:06.720 --> 32:07.640
seriously injured because of him?

32:07.640 --> 32:08.240
Doesn't he have to take responsibility?

32:08.240 --> 32:10.200
You're right about everything, alright?

32:10.200 --> 32:12.240
If I'm right, why are you walking away?

32:12.240 --> 32:14.370
He has to take responsibility! You...

32:15.350 --> 32:16.680
You're so dense.

32:22.720 --> 32:23.750
I'm really sorry.

32:24.590 --> 32:26.750
I couldn't
stop my parents from doing that,

32:26.750 --> 32:28.510
and they've caused you a lot of trouble.

32:28.510 --> 32:29.110
It's okay.

32:29.700 --> 32:31.960
I know you didn't mean for this to happen.

32:35.070 --> 32:35.880
Cheng.

32:38.110 --> 32:39.970
I've liked you since we were kids.

32:40.070 --> 32:42.330
I think you've known that for a long time.

32:42.880 --> 32:43.880
I don't agree with

32:44.070 --> 32:45.200
my parents pressuring you

32:45.200 --> 32:45.830
this way.

32:46.820 --> 32:47.750
But liking you

32:48.720 --> 32:49.920
is my true intention.

32:50.350 --> 32:51.070
Make way!

32:52.440 --> 32:53.500
Make way! Make way!

33:00.590 --> 33:01.110
What?

33:01.790 --> 33:02.960
Getting a love confession from a beauty—

33:02.960 --> 33:03.920
are you flustered?

33:03.920 --> 33:04.680
Or touched?

33:09.750 --> 33:10.830
Jiang Yan, actually...

33:10.830 --> 33:11.440
Alright.

33:12.310 --> 33:13.200
I'm not forcing you

33:13.200 --> 33:14.060
to like me back.

33:15.720 --> 33:17.250
That's not against the law,

33:17.310 --> 33:19.440
and it doesn't affect our work, right?

33:21.160 --> 33:21.690
Let's go.

33:31.920 --> 33:32.380
Mr. Qiu,

33:33.030 --> 33:34.750
the Du family's eldest son,

33:34.750 --> 33:36.400
who had asked about the buyer of the vase

33:36.400 --> 33:38.440
several times before, has come again.

33:38.440 --> 33:39.900
He still wants to meet you.

33:41.000 --> 33:41.590
He said

33:42.110 --> 33:44.240
you should take a look at this first...

33:46.030 --> 33:47.830
then decide whether to meet him.

33:55.750 --> 33:56.950
What was meant to come

33:57.310 --> 33:58.350
has finally come.

34:05.510 --> 34:07.270
He's just an antique dealer.

34:07.550 --> 34:09.190
Why is he so hard to meet?

34:13.510 --> 34:15.110
What did you send him just now?

34:15.110 --> 34:16.239
Will he really come?

34:17.219 --> 34:18.389
If it really is him,

34:19.320 --> 34:20.630
he will definitely come.

34:20.630 --> 34:21.510
Here I am.

34:25.590 --> 34:26.920
Young Master Du, hello.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.550
Ms. Xia, hello.

34:31.480 --> 34:32.710
So you are Mr. Qiu?

34:33.510 --> 34:35.840
Quite hard to get an appointment with you.

34:36.060 --> 34:37.120
Mr. Qiu, seems like

34:37.840 --> 34:39.770
you already knew who I was long ago.

34:40.670 --> 34:43.270
Or perhaps I should call you
by another name...

34:43.880 --> 34:44.590
Xu Zhongyi?

34:53.000 --> 34:53.440
Yes.

34:54.590 --> 34:56.190
Before you knew who I was,

34:56.800 --> 34:57.860
I already knew you.

34:58.590 --> 35:01.450
Thank you for taking care of
my mother all this time.

35:04.920 --> 35:05.650
Please, sit.

35:06.590 --> 35:07.120
Chai Hai,

35:07.710 --> 35:08.510
serve the tea.

35:08.590 --> 35:09.000
Okay.

35:12.720 --> 35:13.770
Should I call you

35:13.800 --> 35:14.880
Xu Zhongyi

35:15.590 --> 35:17.030
or Mr. Qiu?

35:19.280 --> 35:20.280
Poor Granny Yu.

35:20.280 --> 35:22.120
She thought you were struggling
on the run all this time.

35:22.120 --> 35:23.320
But it turns out you've become

35:23.320 --> 35:25.030
quite a big shot now.

35:25.800 --> 35:27.530
You're doing big business here

35:27.960 --> 35:31.020
while letting your own mother
sweep streets back home.

35:31.510 --> 35:32.150
A big shot?

35:33.230 --> 35:34.150
Me—neither one thing

35:34.150 --> 35:34.920
nor another—

35:34.920 --> 35:35.840
a big shot?

35:37.150 --> 35:38.710
Xu Zhongyi is dead.

35:40.000 --> 35:41.130
The one who survived

35:41.360 --> 35:42.440
is Mr. Qiu.

35:44.440 --> 35:45.190
I went back secretly

35:45.190 --> 35:46.850
and checked on her a few times.

35:47.230 --> 35:49.050
But I was too ashamed to reunite with her,

35:49.050 --> 35:50.210
and I didn't dare.

35:51.110 --> 35:51.570
Because

35:52.400 --> 35:54.530
until I kill my enemy with my own hands,

35:54.960 --> 35:56.130
I have no right

35:56.510 --> 35:58.240
to reclaim the name Xu Zhongyi.

35:59.110 --> 36:00.370
What exactly happened

36:01.030 --> 36:02.030
over 20 years ago?

36:03.970 --> 36:07.810
[1967]

36:20.320 --> 36:21.250
Don't be afraid.

36:21.280 --> 36:22.440
Once they get us a boat,

36:22.440 --> 36:24.440
we'll be fine when we reach Nanyang.

36:39.050 --> 36:40.190
Zhongyi, it's me.

36:41.090 --> 36:42.090
The boat is ready.

36:42.400 --> 36:43.530
You can leave today.

36:50.230 --> 36:51.480
It's raining so heavily.

36:51.480 --> 36:52.410
Is the boat safe?

36:56.480 --> 36:57.080
It's safe.

38:21.760 --> 38:23.320
Finding the valuables is the priority.

38:23.320 --> 38:24.720
He's not going to make it.

39:11.760 --> 39:12.560
That bastard—

39:12.840 --> 39:15.040
he lied about helping me
find a boat to Nanyang.

39:15.040 --> 39:17.250
In reality, he was after my antiques.

39:18.070 --> 39:18.870
Fortunately,

39:19.280 --> 39:20.280
I hadn't brought all of them

39:20.280 --> 39:21.110
with me.

39:21.630 --> 39:23.230
I'd buried some beforehand.

39:24.280 --> 39:24.800
Later,

39:25.070 --> 39:26.920
it was those remaining few pieces

39:26.920 --> 39:28.650
that kept me going until today.

39:30.000 --> 39:31.200
I didn't dare go home,

39:31.550 --> 39:33.280
afraid of bringing harm to my family,

39:33.280 --> 39:33.840
so

39:34.280 --> 39:35.440
I changed my identity

39:35.440 --> 39:36.840
and lived under a false name.

39:36.840 --> 39:37.320
Later,

39:37.670 --> 39:39.800
I finally built something for myself.

39:40.070 --> 39:40.870
I stayed here,

39:41.230 --> 39:43.360
just waiting for the day of my revenge.

39:44.480 --> 39:45.880
The bastard he mentioned

39:46.070 --> 39:47.800
is even more ruthless than I am.

39:51.540 --> 39:53.340
You may have been afraid before,

39:53.670 --> 39:55.530
but now it's just pure arrogance.

39:56.360 --> 39:57.190
Since you've already established yourself

39:57.190 --> 39:58.070
as Mr. Qiu

39:58.760 --> 40:00.480
and can live well in Gangdao,

40:01.070 --> 40:02.280
why not go back?

40:04.190 --> 40:05.510
I haven't taken my revenge yet.

40:05.510 --> 40:07.030
I haven't killed my enemy
with my own hands,

40:07.030 --> 40:08.830
so I have no face to see my family.

40:12.150 --> 40:13.230
You have a hundred ways

40:13.230 --> 40:14.800
to seek justice,

40:15.280 --> 40:16.320
yet you chose

40:16.320 --> 40:18.320
the most stubborn and outdated one.

40:18.480 --> 40:19.440
Just look at

40:19.760 --> 40:21.760
what era we're living in—it's the 90s now.

40:21.760 --> 40:23.190
Yet you're still here talking about

40:23.190 --> 40:24.710
killing your enemy with your own hands.

40:24.710 --> 40:25.360
Have you ever thought about

40:25.360 --> 40:26.620
what Granny Yu thinks?

40:27.360 --> 40:28.670
If she knew about this,

40:29.280 --> 40:30.880
what would she want you to do?

40:35.550 --> 40:36.150
I'm sorry.

40:36.800 --> 40:38.000
I can't truly

40:38.000 --> 40:39.400
put myself in your shoes,

40:39.480 --> 40:40.320
but at the same time,

40:40.320 --> 40:43.120
you've never really considered
Granny Yu either.

40:43.400 --> 40:45.630
I still have a conference
to attend in Jiangcheng,

40:45.630 --> 40:46.760
so I can stay here

40:46.760 --> 40:48.710
until tomorrow afternoon at the latest.

40:48.710 --> 40:49.360
Whether you want

40:49.360 --> 40:51.160
to go back with me to see Granny Yu

40:51.400 --> 40:52.510
is up to you.

40:57.150 --> 40:58.210
Mr. Qiu, I heard you

40:58.400 --> 41:00.060
hold an antique auction here.

41:00.400 --> 41:02.000
I'd love to see it for myself.

41:02.190 --> 41:04.000
I need to pick out a gift

41:04.000 --> 41:05.280
for my project's property consultant.

41:05.280 --> 41:07.280
Mr. Qiu, why don't you take me there?

41:07.400 --> 41:07.800
Okay.

41:08.960 --> 41:09.890
It's just ahead.

41:10.630 --> 41:11.190
Let's go.

41:13.670 --> 41:14.200
Let's go.

41:15.400 --> 41:16.030
Bidder 11

41:16.150 --> 41:18.230
bids $1.1 million. Going twice!

41:18.710 --> 41:19.360
Bidder 11

41:19.400 --> 41:21.630
bids $1.1 million. Going three times!

41:22.030 --> 41:23.110
Sold!

41:23.550 --> 41:24.480
Congratulations

41:24.480 --> 41:25.710
on winning this

41:25.760 --> 41:27.550
rare and precious

41:27.800 --> 41:29.710
Yuan Dynasty octagonal "Yuhuchun" vase

41:29.710 --> 41:31.570
with an underglaze-red dragon motif.

41:31.570 --> 41:32.770
The one on the far side

41:32.800 --> 41:34.400
is that loser, Du Zhaoji.

41:34.480 --> 41:35.880
Please have the item

41:36.070 --> 41:37.150
packaged and delivered

41:37.150 --> 41:38.920
to VIP No. 11's storage.

41:39.400 --> 41:40.150
Thank you.

41:41.080 --> 41:42.120
So next,

41:42.150 --> 41:43.280
let's move on

41:43.320 --> 41:44.670
to our second piece.

41:45.030 --> 41:46.030
Someone you know?

41:46.040 --> 41:47.810
A very rare and precious piece.

41:47.840 --> 41:48.320
No.

41:48.550 --> 41:50.710
It's also from the Yuan Dynasty.

41:51.070 --> 41:52.270
Please, bring it out.

41:58.360 --> 41:59.480
The second lot

41:59.510 --> 42:02.840
is a Yuan Dynasty hand-painted
Persian blue-rimmed basin.

42:03.110 --> 42:05.510
The starting bid is $500,000.

42:10.230 --> 42:13.400
Bidder 3, $550,000, first call.

42:13.630 --> 42:14.650
Any other bids?

42:14.800 --> 42:15.630
Here, Bidder 7.

42:15.630 --> 42:16.090
Mr. Qiu,

42:16.440 --> 42:17.590
how did Ms. Xia manage to

42:17.590 --> 42:19.050
find you here so suddenly?

42:19.480 --> 42:21.140
Naturally, someone told her.

42:21.880 --> 42:22.680
It's a warning

42:23.320 --> 42:25.760
that he already knows my weakness.

42:27.110 --> 42:28.170
It doesn't matter.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.880
Isn't the basis of mutual exploitation

42:29.880 --> 42:31.010
that each side holds

42:31.150 --> 42:32.610
something over the other?

42:33.760 --> 42:34.490
Fair enough.

42:37.030 --> 42:39.230
Bidder 3, $750,000, second call!

42:42.920 --> 42:43.650
Comrade Xia,

42:44.240 --> 42:45.190
I finally found you.

42:45.190 --> 42:46.230
I'm so happy.

42:47.440 --> 42:48.280
Ye Xiaoqiong?

42:49.190 --> 42:49.840
I never expected

42:49.840 --> 42:51.110
to see you in Gangdao.

42:51.630 --> 42:53.280
Looks like you're doing well.

42:53.280 --> 42:54.630
Didn't you say you were going to Hushi

42:54.630 --> 42:55.960
to look for your family?

42:56.190 --> 42:57.710
There was no family to find.

42:57.710 --> 42:58.480
After staying in Hushi

42:58.480 --> 42:59.710
for a while,

42:59.760 --> 43:01.760
I eventually made my way to Gangdao.

43:01.880 --> 43:02.480
I got lucky

43:02.760 --> 43:05.090
and landed a job
as a clerk in a big company.

43:09.800 --> 43:10.700
If back then

43:10.760 --> 43:11.760
you hadn't rescued me

43:11.760 --> 43:12.960
from those traffickers

43:12.960 --> 43:13.620
on the train

43:14.190 --> 43:15.190
and lent me money,

43:15.670 --> 43:17.070
I probably would've lost

43:17.230 --> 43:18.360
all hope in life.

43:19.030 --> 43:20.280
So, your kindness

43:20.480 --> 43:21.280
can never be repaid

43:21.280 --> 43:22.320
with money.

43:23.280 --> 43:24.150
I originally thought about

43:24.150 --> 43:25.480
wiring the money to you,

43:25.760 --> 43:26.830
but I felt

43:26.960 --> 43:28.190
I had to thank you

43:28.510 --> 43:29.630
in person.

43:30.190 --> 43:31.120
So, Comrade Xia,

43:31.280 --> 43:32.410
please accept this.

43:36.630 --> 43:37.110
No need.

43:38.190 --> 43:39.850
Just repay what you borrowed.

43:39.920 --> 43:41.000
I only lent you

43:41.000 --> 43:41.960
100 yuan back then.

43:41.960 --> 43:43.440
It was barely enough for travel expenses.

43:43.440 --> 43:44.670
It was your own hard work

43:44.670 --> 43:45.320
that got you

43:45.320 --> 43:46.580
this decent job today.

43:48.030 --> 43:48.960
Actually,

43:49.800 --> 43:51.030
I didn't come to you today

43:51.030 --> 43:52.230
just to catch up.

43:53.590 --> 43:54.670
Do you have time

43:54.670 --> 43:55.400
to talk?
